      "writtenOn": "2026-07-02T15:34:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "can we come up with a better name than GenerateV2? perhaps something to hint at the fact that this takes the full openapi structure as a value, whereas the old Generate just expects a value with a flat structure of schemas?",
      "revId": "6f59a356d0a7ec1fb5ac642b0223a27f7a041c6b",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "df944c9b_7a021918",
        "filename": "encoding/openapi/generate_v2.go",
        "patchSetId": 1
      },
      "lineNbr": 152,
      "author": {
        "id": 1007275
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-03T12:25:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I went with GenerateV2 to indicate that this is not just intended to be a variation of Generate but a full replacement, and Generate will be deprecated and removed in time. GenerateV2 can do anything that Generate does, so I\u0027m reasonably OK with the name as is. Alternative suggestions?",
      "parentUuid": "b812feb8_6d15fecd",
      "revId": "6f59a356d0a7ec1fb5ac642b0223a27f7a041c6b",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
    },
