      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-03T13:45:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Fair enough. I guess it\u0027s fine to use \"V2\" names when we don\u0027t feel like an entirely new v2 package is necessary. I don\u0027t have a particularly better name in mind.",
      "parentUuid": "df944c9b_7a021918",
      "revId": "6f59a356d0a7ec1fb5ac642b0223a27f7a041c6b",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
